item.title: Error_game_js5io
item.dc:creator: @OMG_its_NICK OMG its NICK
item.description:
@OMG_its_NICK wrote:

How to fix this error: I have uploaded cache508 here http://www.filefront.com/14344337/cache508.rar for all of you guys that might need it. You will need winrar to unpack it, but you all should have it :P. Download this, extract it, and then move the cache508 folder to C:\cache508. And I don’t mean make a new folder called cache508 in C:. I mean move the one off your desktop there. So when you go to C:\cache508 you will see a rs2 folder, not another cache508. Hope this helps! This should solve this problem.
